Deti? chudym ne
Populace by see mela regulovat. Proc sse neudela zakon, kde by dite. Meli jen
lide s urcittym prijmem a meeli by neejake bydleni. Pri poruseni by platili
pokutu treba sto nebo dveste tisic a nemeli by naa ditte pridavky. Jo bezdaci a
zebraci se nemwj co mnozit, dite nessmi trpet hlady
